icationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">1 Day Commercial River Trips</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1906936\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>Smooth Water Raft Trips</h2>\n<p>Half-day, and full-day smooth water raft trips on the Colorado River from Lees Ferry to Horseshoe Bend and back are provided by <a href=\"https://www.riveradventures.com/horseshoe-bend-rafting-trips/horseshoe-bend-rafting-experience/half-day/\" id=\"https://www.riveradventures.com/horseshoe-bend-rafting-trips/horseshoe-bend-rafting-experience/half-day/|\">Wilderness River Adventures</a>.<br/>\n<br/>\nTrips begin in Page, Arizona. Participants are then bused to Lee’s Ferry where they meet their river guide. Highlights of the trip include: motoring the 10 miles upriver to Petroglyph Beach to explore archaeological sites while experiencing the majestic sandstone cliffs rising on both sides of the river, The return bus ride to Page passes by the Vermilion Cliffs, Marble Canyon, and crosses over the river on Navajo Bridge.<br/>\n</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_2425212\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2425212\"><div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup CaptionedImage\">\n<figure class=\"-auto-width\">\n<img alt=\"Looking down from the top of a sheer sandstone cliff at a green river at the bottom. Foliage growing along the shoreline.\" src=\"/grca/planyourvisit/images/DSC_8590.jpg?maxwidth=1300&amp;maxheight=1300&amp;autorotate=false&amp;format=webp\" title=\"Colorado River in Glen Canyon National Recreation Area beyond Horseshoe Bend.\"/>\n<figcaption>Smooth water raft trips take place on the Colorado River between Glen Canyon Dam and Lees Ferry. <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS/M. Quinn</p></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5112393\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5112393\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h2>Additional river info can be found on the following webpages</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"\" summary=\"table containing links for river trip information\" width=\"700px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"\" valign=\"top\"><strong>Commercial River Trips (River Concessioners)</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/one-day-river-trip.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1906934,one-day-river-trip.htm,11006|\">1 Day River Trips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/river-concessioners.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1906904,river-concessioners.htm,11006|\">3-18 Day River Trips</a></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"\" valign=\"top\"><strong>Noncommercial (Private) River Trips</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/overview-diamond-ck.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1932929,overview-diamond-ck.htm,11006|\">2-5 Day River Trips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/overview-lees-ferry-diamond-ck.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1931507,overview-lees-ferry-diamond-ck.htm,11006|\">12-25 Day River Trips</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/river-faq.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1937558,river-faq.htm,11006|\">River FAQs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/river_support.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1937759,river_support.htm,11006|\">River Trip Support Companies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/weightedlottery.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1932935,weightedlottery.htm,11006|\">Weighted Lottery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/noncommercial-riv-docs.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2102042,noncommercial-riv-docs.htm,11006|\">Helpful Links</a></li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: March 12, 2025</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
